<C>__{eric}
<D>__{try harder. try again.}
<A>__{shifting angle eric nears tin tin as tin tin throws another knife. eric closing in. he claps hand together, immobilizing the next knife. opens his hands, almost an "oops" gesture. keeps on coming. angle eric and tin tin as they meet. tin tin attempts a roundhouse. eric blocks it and smashes tin tin into the alley wall.}
